import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { Playground } from 'docz'
import Stage from '../stage'
import { Rope } from '../index'

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"rope"}}>{`Rope`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"props"}}>{`Props`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="p" props={{"href":"http://pixijs.download/dev/docs/PIXI.mesh.Rope.html"}}>{`http://pixijs.download/dev/docs/PIXI.mesh.Rope.html`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"usage"}}>{`Usage`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={0} __code={`<Stage width={500} height={300} options={{ backgroundColor: 0xeef1f5 }}>
  <Rope
    points={[
      new PIXI.Point(0, 150),
      new PIXI.Point(100, 100),
      new PIXI.Point(150, 150),
      new PIXI.Point(200, 100),
      new PIXI.Point(400, 150),
    ]}
    image={\'https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/s.cdpn.io/693612/snake.png\'}
  />
</Stage>`} __scope={{props,Stage,Rope}}>
  <Stage width={500} height={300} options={{ backgroundColor: 0xeef1f5 }}>
    <Rope
      points={
        [
          new PIXI.Point(0, 150),
          new PIXI.Point(100, 100),
          new PIXI.Point(150, 150),
          new PIXI.Point(200, 100),
          new PIXI.Point(400, 150),
        ]
      }
      image={'https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/s.cdpn.io/693612/snake.png'} />
  </Stage>
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"example"}}>{`Example`}</MDXTag>
<iframe 
  height={500} 
  scrolling="no"
  title="Container" 
  src="//codepen.io/inlet/embed/aecfbdab7d8d320d2ae19ca800d77594/?height=300&theme-id=33987&default-tab=result&embed-version=2"
  frameBorder="no" 
  allowransparency="true"
  allowFullScreen="true"
  style={{ width: '100%' }} /></MDXTag>
